  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >First you got sand in your shoes, and now you've spilled your nice cold drink all over your suit. That's just your luck. Right as you were about to enjoy some downtime on the beach you get sucked into a tube, sending you directly toward yet another mission. But not to worry—this is the mission you've been waiting for: the final chapter in stopping your arch-nemesis. So tidy up that suit because you've got a world to save!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206980/extras/863c0a0c115182683594fa0fd76d9e75.webp?t=1741710098\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206980/extras/863c0a0c115182683594fa0fd76d9e75.poster.avif?t=1741710098\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=148 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Secret Agent Puzzle you step into the sandy shoes of the world's best agent. You're hot on the trail of Dr. Von Bösenstein, and the only thing standing in your way is a series of puzzle rooms. What's that? Very deadly puzzle rooms? More than 50 of them? Great. I'm sure you'll do fine!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SOLVE ROOMS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Think ahead as you move through each room one step at a time. Find the correct sequence, or find yourself digging an early grave instead.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206980/extras/21abce594fcd05fa408f0b78d295c783.poster.avif?t=1741710098\" width=616 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206980/extras/21abce594fcd05fa408f0b78d295c783.webm?t=1741710098\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206980/extras/21abce594fcd05fa408f0b78d295c783.mp4?t=1741710098\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >AVOID TRAPS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Spike beds, sleeping gas, lasers, and even sharks. Anything a cartoon villain could ever dream of will be thrown your way. Better deactivate each trap and stop Dr. Von Bösenstein fast, before she invents something even more bothersome... like laser sharks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206980/extras/7852eb31cb230742a480acde22581449.poster.avif?t=1741710098\" width=616 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206980/extras/7852eb31cb230742a480acde22581449.webm?t=1741710098\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206980/extras/7852eb31cb230742a480acde22581449.mp4?t=1741710098\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DISCOVER THE TRUTH</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find out what else Dr. Von Bösenstein is scheming-a world-ending disaster, no doubt.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206980/extras/cfd8ae8f7d208b0cbdaacd03b54040d1.poster.avif?t=1741710098\" width=616 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206980/extras/cfd8ae8f7d208b0cbdaacd03b54040d1.webm?t=1741710098\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206980/extras/cfd8ae8f7d208b0cbdaacd03b54040d1.mp4?t=1741710098\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206980/extras/8ba92409b867a4582e9ec17f2d9df59a.apng?t=1741710098\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206980/extras/8ba92409b867a4582e9ec17f2d9df59a.poster.avif?t=1741710098\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=148 /></picture></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Pixel art meticulously extracted from the best memories of a '90s kid,  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > A story rich with comedy, handcrafted from the totally classified pile of sticky notes on my desk,</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 6 unique chapters taking you to locations all over the world,  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Over 50 rooms to rack your brain over,  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > A white fluffy cat—albeit a grumpy one.  </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206980/extras/ea22dee0123acaab707d7c4b080e51f3.apng?t=1741710098\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206980/extras/ea22dee0123acaab707d7c4b080e51f3.poster.avif?t=1741710098\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=64 /></picture></span></p>",
